content:
Merge Duplicate Cases from the Cases List View

You can merge cases from the Cases list view.

Available in: Lightning Experience
Essentials, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions


To view cases:	Read on cases
To create cases:	Create on cases
To edit cases:	Edit on cases
To delete cases:	Delete on cases

Go to the Cases list view.
Select up to three cases you want to merge.
Click Merge Cases.
The Compare cases model is displayed.
Select the master case and field values for the master record.
Click Next.
Click Merge.
The cases are merged into a master case.
title: Merge Duplicate Cases in Service Cloud
